    ├── expenses/
    │   └── index.tsx           ← Expenses view
    ├── settings/
    │   └── index.tsx           ← Settings view
    ├── onboarding/
    │   └── index.tsx           ← Onboarding wizard
    ├── notifications/
    │   └── index.tsx           ← Notifications
    └── _layout.tsx             ← Root layout (providers)

  □ Build custom bottom tab bar matching web's bottom-nav:
    - 5 tabs: Dashboard, Shifts, Analytics, Goals, More
    - Icons: use lucide-react-native (home, calendar, trending-up, trophy, layout-grid)
    - Active state: brand color (#10b981) with label visible
    - Inactive state: muted color
  □ Build header component matching web's app-header:
    - Left: Avatar initials circle
    - Center: Platform tabs switcher (scrollable horizontal)
    - Right: Clock, Notifications bell (with badge), Settings gear
  □ Wire the "More" tab to open a bottom sheet (using @gorhom/bottom-sheet)
    matching web's openMoreNavMenu drawer

VALIDATION:
